              <h3>Thank You!</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
              <p>Thank you for your order. Your items will arrive in the mail 2-3 in business days.</p>
              <p>Your confirmation number is: <span id = "confirm_num"> Confirmation number Here</span></p>
